# Versioning Policy

SentinelGRC follows Semantic Versioning.

Examples:

| Version | Meaning                         |
| ------- | ------------------------------- |
| 0.1.0   | Initial framework release       |
| 0.2.0   | New functionality added         |
| 0.2.1   | Bug fixes only                  |
| 0.3.0   | Framework mapping enhancements  |
| 1.0.0   | First stable production release |
| 2.0.0   | Breaking architectural changes  |

---

# Support Lifecycle

Development releases (`0.x.x`) may introduce architectural changes while the framework evolves.

Beginning with **1.0.0**, releases will prioritize backward compatibility, documented upgrade paths, and database migration support.

